Title="Haros - Isthia Village"

[TranslatorEvent0]
Message="My Log: So this is planet Haros, home of the Krall. Why is the gate unguarded? It's really gorgeous and lush. I see towering mountains covered with ice. It's quite cool."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent1]
Message="After the invasion of Madehiten, some of us went to Exploited in order to join with them and destroy the Krall. We took a village here on Haros, but soon the Krall threw us back. Some of us managed to hide in the church and locked both doors."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent2]
Message="Mr. Paci has an interesting gift. He is highly intelligent and well respected. He is also a heavy metal musician."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent3]
Message="I managed to lock the church up and throw the key into a house. I hope this helps. There are hundreds of Krall outside, so I ran here to hide."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent4]
Message="They drove us back to the gate, but we've fortified it and tried to fight them back."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent5]
Message="The situation has gone bad. The occupation of Madehiten failed. We even lost Exploited, and the important alliance with the Skaarj is lost forever. We retain only our home planet, Haros."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent6]
Message="We will soon need the help of our allies, the Brutes. They inhabit the planet Pharao, but we can't contact them. The library where the location was stored was burned, and no one remembers."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent7]
Message="My Log: I hope that some of the people who were there survived."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent8]
Message="It says the Capital city Machellopolis is located about 10km from here. Then it mentions catacombs beneath it. An entire system of tunnels that lead into the surrounding buildings."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent9]
Message="My Log: No one is here. I need to find the secret door. There could be a survivor."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent10]
Message="Sadly, most of us were killed. A few survivors are trapped in the church. At least, we've found a Flak Cannon. Sid says that there is a secret exit. I need to find it."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

[TranslatorEvent11]
Message="My Log: I remember there was a secret entrance in the church. If there is one, it will be right here."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent12]
Message="The planet is mostly occupied by Krall. We managed to get here from Haros, but the Krall attacked us strongly. I hope that we manage to get away."
M_NewMessage="Krall notes"
M_TransMessage="Krall notes"

